extends ../layout

block content
  section#battle-of-the-birds.section
    .container
      h2 Battle of the Birds

      p.
        Battle of the Birds is our annual fundraiser held each year during the Seahawks–Eagles
        rivalry game. It's a friendly competition between the Yellowstone Sea Hawkers and our
        local Eagles fan counterparts — where the real winners are the families we support.

      h3 Benefiting Billings Family Service
      p.
        All proceeds from Battle of the Birds go directly to
        #[a(href="https://billingsfamilyservice.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Billings Family Service],
        a nonprofit dedicated to strengthening families and individuals across the Yellowstone
        Valley through counseling, education, and support programs.

  section.section.alt-bg
    .container
      h3 How to Participate
      .cards.cards-three
        .card
          .card-body
            h3 Attend the Watch Party
            p Join us for the game and cheer on the Hawks. Entry fees and donations go to the cause.
        .card
          .card-body
            h3 Donate Directly
            p Can't make it? You can still support Billings Family Service with a direct donation.
            a.btn-outline(href="https://billingsfamilyservice.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Visit Billings Family Service
        .card
          .card-body
            h3 Spread the Word
            p Tell your friends and family about the event. Every bit of awareness helps.

  section.section
    .container
      a.btn-outline(href="/#charitable") &larr; Back to Charitable Work
